Dependency Information

Apache Maven

<dependency>
  <groupId>at.rseiler</groupId>
  <artifactId>lcmip</artifactId>
  <version>1.0</version>
  <type>pom</type>
</dependency>

Apache Buildr

'at.rseiler:lcmip:pom:1.0'

Apache Ant

<dependency org="at.rseiler" name="lcmip" rev="1.0">
  <artifact name="lcmip" type="pom" />
</dependency>

Groovy Grape

@Grapes(
@Grab(group='at.rseiler', module='lcmip', version='1.0')
)

Grails

compile 'at.rseiler:lcmip:1.0'

Leiningen

[at.rseiler/lcmip "1.0"]

SBT
